# Crypto Specs & Legal Framing

- FORBID UI text claiming "mathematical certainty of truth" or "absolute anti-deepfake". Use terms like "tamper-evident", "authenticity heuristics", and "risk reduction".
- REQUIRE legal disclaimers on PDF generation indicating the document "supports workflow and disclosure but does not guarantee admissibility under FRE 902."
- REQUIRE explicit interface documentation (Inputs, Outputs, Expected Failure Modes) for `VaultEncryptionHandler` and `CourierCrypto`.
